    <ol>
    <li>Edit your nostr profile</li>
    <li>Enter <strong id="success-username">username@nostr.industries</strong> into the NIP-05 identifier field</li>
    <li>Save your profile</li>
    </ol>
    Congratulations, you are verified! <img src="favicon.png" class="mini-badge" alt="verification badge" />
  </div>
</div>

